Package: APCplot
Type: Package
Version: 0.2.2
Date: 2024-02-27
Title: Triangular Age-Period-Cohort surfaces
Description: Plot age-period-cohort surfaces (rates and rate ratios) on a grid
   of equilateral triangles using Martin R Smith's Ternary package. An ancillary
   function is provided to set up datasets from the Human Mortality Database for
   use by APCplot.
URL: https://github.com/BugBunny/APCplot
Author: Ian Timaeus <ian.timaeus@lshtm.ac.uk> [aut, cre] (0000-0001-8011-4806)
Maintainer: Ian Timaeus <ian.timaeus@lshtm.ac.uk>
Depends:
    R (>= 2.10),
    Ternary
Imports:
   HMDHFDplus,
   PlotTools,
   viridisLite
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
